When will we use F1-score instead of precision(accuracy)? 

F1 score 是recall跟precision的平均
當recall與precision的值差很多時，就可以用F1 score衡量

Why don’t we use binary classification function as the activation function in neural networks? 

f(x)在x=0時不連續
所以在backprop的時候無法微分

What is the bias and variance of a machine learning algorithm? 
bias 越大underfitting越嚴重

variance  越大overfitting越嚴重



What is one-hot encoding? 
用0與1表示無序的特徵
讓每一個特徵與原點的距離一樣


How to prevent overfitting in neural networks? (write down anything you know) 

1.dropout
2.collect more data
3.make sure training data and validation data are from same distribution
4.regularization (L1,L2…)


